# SkillTok Implementation Plan

We are going to build **SkillTok**, a mobile-first, short-video learning platform web application. We'll build a responsive web application that provides an app-like experience (similar to TikTok/Reels) focused on micro-learning. 

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Since the original tech stack suggested React Native/Flutter for a mobile app, I propose we build this as a **Next.js Web Application** designed with a mobile-first "app-like" UI. This ensures it's easily accessible on all devices while still feeling like a native mobile app. Please confirm if this approach works for you!

> [!NOTE]
> We will be utilizing **Vanilla CSS** with a robust design system to achieve the requested modern, glassmorphic, and dynamic look with a sleek dark mode.

